{"tid":681522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強衝車廂易釀禍　(中國)滬女遭列車拖行亡","createTime":"2018-05-28T06:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T10:16:32.000Z","uid":53026,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"897127af8ce79ab5fba5cb31ddcd9543dc87864e","tid":681522,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"強衝車廂易釀禍　(中國)滬女遭列車拖行亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180528/large/28cb4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180528%2Flarge%2F28cb4p.jpg&h=e346af46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■(中國)上海女子被夾在月台閘門和列車之間。<br />\n<br />\n【地鐵意外】<br />\n【本報訊】乘客趕時間衝上地鐵的案例，比比皆是，過往亦曾發生致命案件。有(中國)上海有女子在車門關閉前將手伸進大門，想強行開門上車，最終被大門夾着，地鐵開車後將她撞向安全護欄身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180528/large/28cb555p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180528%2Flarge%2F28cb555p.jpg&h=10fc5e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■(中國)重慶男乘輕軌強行衝門頸部被夾住。互聯網<br />\n(中國)重慶男被車門夾頸<br />\n<br />\n在(中國)上海寶安公路地鐵站，上月有女子在車門快關上時，用手強行拉開月台幕門，打算衝上地鐵，豈料車門已經關上，女子夾在地鐵閘門與月台幕門之間，此時高速行駛的列車呼呼駛來，不時撞到女子手中的物品，嚇得她緊緊貼着幕門站，非常危險。當時有地鐵工作人員表示，有人被夾在車門和幕門之間，防夾裝置是無法感應到。<br />\n不過，另一名(中國)上海女子卻沒那麼幸運，她在2010年將手伸入地鐵大門，想強行上車，最終大門夾着手腕。此時地鐵列車啟動，並拖行該女子，加速時將她重擊到安全護欄，反彈跌落在月台上，該女子最終因搶救無效死亡。(中國)重慶亦發生過類似案件，一名男子在車廂內奪門而出，不料「頭過人未過」，大門夾着該人頸部，動彈不得。幸好車長沒有開車，他最終沒有大礙。<br />\n香港較少出現衝閘而成的意外，但香港月台空隙過闊，屢遭非議。在2016月11月，一名婆婆在羅湖站下車時疑「叉錯腳」墮軌，「大字形」跌在路軌上面，幸好及早發現，婆婆只是輕微受傷。港鐵曾表示，在部份車站安裝了感應器，一旦路面突然出現重力物品，會立即通知列車，防止意外。"},{"pid":"7b27a6a6c20ff1663c55bdb6662ef9886270633a","tid":681522,"uid":101396,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"香港既幕門應該學煙盒貼呢啲廣告"},{"pid":"a1c793e98ae4bd01489f0c4ad05a3f874871cdc0","tid":681522,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"有幕門都出事，不如慳返啦"},{"pid":"910133399b063d14f9fcfc4392e95bc04b91b340","tid":681522,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"香港改用支那車廂，就可以玩夾娃娃了"},{"pid":"efda5ef4913cd32edf3b3feceb9f9ac3a255184a","tid":681522,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"張圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0552d775095e4aec9c150f2bf1d686e82a8135","tid":681522,"uid":15483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"衝多D啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090d924b423d1bfa55504c9647758bca860b9827","tid":681522,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"用手強行拉開月台幕門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e2e0016a76d9e11c4c881ce7c3bc542c975b36","tid":681522,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/161602_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F161602_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif&h=e7d88790&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0395d29e19cd1b230040934b9789afd61abd6569","tid":681522,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"夾住左個人都無alert照開車，又嬴"},{"pid":"78486eed4c16e2ae11c613645efe2ce908ae1455","tid":681522,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180427/58119407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F58119407&d=dkh7bE%2B2t6lWS